text: Abryutino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Yekimovskoye Rural Settlement of Ryazansky District, Ryazan Oblast, Russia. The population was 13 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == The village is located 16 km south-west from Ryazan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ryazan Oblast
title: Abryutino
